
    A cop from Umbumbulu KwaZulu Natal (KZN) was killed on his
way to work allegedly by four suspects that were following him. The suspects opened fire on the cop fatally wounding him, the
suspects fled the scene afterwards.According to cops they traced the suspects to Esikhaleni in
KZN after intensive investigations, the appeared in the Eshowe Magistrate’s
